# challenge: named pipes

📅 2025-07-29
📁 practicing piping

---

## ✅ what i did  
-clicked start
-opened the terminal
-ran: 'mkfifo /tmp/flag_fifo'
-ran: '/challenge/run > /tmp/flag_fifo &'
-ran: 'cat /tmp/flag_fifo'
-flag popped out

## 🧑🏾‍🏫 what this challenge teaches u
how to use fifos to sync processes and pass data without saving it to disk
mkfifo makes the pipe, and & runs the writer in background so the reader can unblock it

